{"word":"G5496 - χειραγωγέω - cheiragōgéō - khi-rag-ogue-eh'-o - Lead by the hand","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χειραγωγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">cheiragōgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khi-rag-ogue-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lead by the hand</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கைலாகுகொடு"},{"paragraph":"to lead by the hand"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5497 - χειραγωγός - cheiragōgós - khi-rag-o-gos'/5497\">G5497</a>; to be a <i>hand leader</i>, that is, to <i>guide</i> (a blind person): - lead by the hand.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5495/5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496/5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497/5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498/5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499/5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5500/5500\">G5500</a>, <a href=\"#/G886/886\">G886</a>"}]}